{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><i>10pm, September 4th, 1997.</i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The reclusive Detective Lambda is contacted by the F.B.I. to consult on a deadly case of arson. Can Lambda bring down the charismatic cult leader at the center of the mystery? It's time for the ultimate battle of wits! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Daemon Masquerade is a supernatural detective game inspired by anime like Death Note and Fate/stay night, and games such as the Ace Attorney series.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Organize the Evidence</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2277120/extras/Organize.gif?t=1730340876\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Meticulously sort the clues on your pinboard however you see fit. Do you prefer the neat orderly rows of a professional detective, or the scattered piles of a conspiracy theorist? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Annotate your Thoughts</strong><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2277120/extras/Drawing_2.gif?t=1730340876\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There's no need to fetch a pen and paper, scribble your notes directly onto the evidence!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Deduce the Truth</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2277120/extras/Thread_of_Logic_3.gif?t=1730340876\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> The Thread of Logic deduction system allows you to solve cases in multiple ways, just as long as you've got the facts to back up your theories.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item